def update(self, index, val):


🎯 Goal

Change one value in the array.

🔍 How it works

• Move down to the correct leaf
• Update its value
• While returning back:

Recalculate parent sums

Only one path from root → leaf is visited.

If tree height is log n → time is log n.

🧠 Mental Map

“Go to the leaf.
Fix sums while climbing back.”

