• Build → O(n)
• Update → O(log n)
• Range Query → O(log n)
• Space → O(n)

🚀 When Is Segment Tree Used?

1️⃣ Range Sum Queries
2️⃣ Range Minimum / Maximum
3️⃣ Dynamic array problems
4️⃣ Competitive programming
5️⃣ Any problem with:

Many updates

Many range queries

